---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Contrato Firmado - EMED"
    description="Tu contrato ha sido firmado y enviado exitosamente."
>
    <div class="bg-crema min-h-screen">
        <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-32">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-2xl">
                <div
                    class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center"
                >
                    <!-- Success icon -->
                    <div
                        class="mx-auto mb-6 w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center animate-scale-in"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-10 h-10 text-green-500"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2.5"
                                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>

                    <h1
                        class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4"
                    >
                        ¡Gracias por firmar tu contrato!
                    </h1>

                    <p
                        class="text-gray-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6"
                    >
                        Hemos recibido exitosamente tu contrato de capacitación
                        firmado electrónicamente, junto con los documentos
                        adjuntos requeridos.
                    </p>

                    <div
                        class="bg-celeste/5 border border-celeste/20 rounded-xl p-5 mb-8 text-left"
                    >
                        <h3
                            class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center text-sm md:text-base"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-5 h-5 text-celeste mr-2 flex-shrink-0"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                            ¿Qué sigue?
                        </h3>
                        <ol
                            class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 list-decimal pl-5"
                        >
                            <li>
                                Recibirás un <strong
                                    >correo de confirmación</strong
                                > con el resumen de tu contrato.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Nuestro equipo <strong
                                    >revisará tu documentación</strong
                                > en las próximas horas hábiles.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Te contactaremos para <strong
                                    >coordinar los siguientes pasos</strong
                                > de tu proceso de inscripción.
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
                        <a
                            href="/"
                            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all duration-200"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                            Volver al inicio
                        </a>
                        <a
                            href="https://wa.me/56965620939?text=Hola,%20acabo%20de%20firmar%20mi%20contrato%20en%20la%20web"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="whatsapp-link inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                                fill="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                            Escríbenos por WhatsApp
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    @keyframes scale-in {
        0% {
            transform: scale(0);
            opacity: 0;
        }
        70% {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        100% {
            transform: scale(1);
            opacity: 1;
        }
    }
    .animate-scale-in {
        animation: scale-in 0.5s ease-out forwards;
    }

    .whatsapp-link {
        background-color: #22c55e !important;
        color: white !important;
    }
    .whatsapp-link:hover {
        background-color: #16a34a !important;
    }
</style>
